---
import LayoutRedesign from '../layouts/LayoutRedesign.astro';
---

<LayoutRedesign
  title="Private AI Support & Success"
  description="Understand the white-glove onboarding, monitoring, and ongoing optimization included with intent solutions io deployments."
>

  <!-- SECTION 1: Hero + Support Fundamentals (IMAGE BACKGROUND) -->
  <section class="support-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="section-badge">SUPPORT</p>
        <h1 class="hero-title">
          White-glove <span class="highlight-box">support</span> from kickoff through scale
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-description">
          Private AI adoption is a journey. We partner with your teams using hands-on onboarding, 24/7 monitoring, and proactive
          optimization reviews so the platform stays reliable and operators stay confident.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Support Fundamentals Grid -->
      <div class="fundamentals-grid">
        <div class="fundamental-card">
          <h3>White-glove onboarding</h3>
          <p>
            Guided rollout, team training, and documentation customized for your playbooks ensure day-one adoption.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="fundamental-card">
          <h3>24/7 monitoring</h3>
          <p>
            Automated health checks and on-call engineers keep availability on track around the clock.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="fundamental-card">
          <h3>Guaranteed response</h3>
          <p>
            4-hour standard SLA and 1-hour enterprise SLA for critical incidents, communicated via your preferred channels.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="fundamental-card">
          <h3>Monthly reviews</h3>
          <p>
            Optimization sessions walk through usage trends, backlog priorities, and roadmap adjustments.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="fundamental-card">
          <h3>Shared tooling</h3>
          <p>
            Ticketing, alerting, and dashboards live in shared portals so you have the same visibility we do.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="fundamental-card">
          <h3>Change management</h3>
          <p>
            Structured comms plans, stakeholder briefings, and release notes keep leadership and operators aligned.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 2: Onboarding Timeline + Support Channels (DARK + TEAL WAVE) -->
  <section class="support-onboarding">
    <!-- Teal wave background -->
    <div class="wave-background">
      <svg class="wave wave-1" viewBox="0 0 1440 320" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <path fill="rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.3)" d="M0,192L48,197.3C96,203,192,213,288,229.3C384,245,480,267,576,250.7C672,235,768,181,864,181.3C960,181,1056,235,1152,234.7C1248,235,1344,181,1392,154.7L1440,128L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"></path>
      </svg>
      <svg class="wave wave-2" viewBox="0 0 1440 320" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <path fill="rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.2)" d="M0,64L48,80C96,96,192,128,288,128C384,128,480,96,576,90.7C672,85,768,107,864,144C960,181,1056,235,1152,234.7C1248,235,1344,181,1392,154.7L1440,128L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="onboarding-grid">
        <div class="onboarding-timeline">
          <h2><span class="highlight-box">Onboarding</span> timeline</h2>
          <ol class="timeline-list">
            <li>Kickoff workshop to align goals, success metrics, and rollout teams.</li>
            <li>Hands-on configuration sessions covering infrastructure, models, and integrations.</li>
            <li>Role-based enablement training with live exercises and certification checklists.</li>
            <li>Launch support window with office hours and rapid iteration on feedback.</li>
          </ol>
          <p class="timeline-note">
            You receive playbooks, recorded sessions, and quick-reference guides so future hires can onboard with minimal friction.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="support-channels-card">
          <h3>Support <span class="highlight-box">channels</span></h3>
          <ul class="channels-list">
            <li>Dedicated Slack or Teams channel with direct engineer access.</li>
            <li>Ticket queue integrated with Jira, Linear, or your ITSM platform.</li>
            <li>Emergency hotline for severity one incidents when minutes matter.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="channels-note">
            Prefer a different workflow? We adapt to email, SMS, or PagerDuty based on your escalation policies.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 3: Continuous Improvement + Meet the Team (IMAGE BACKGROUND) -->
  <section class="support-improvement">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        Continuous <span class="highlight-box">improvement</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="improvement-grid">
        <div class="improvement-card">
          <h3>Usage analytics</h3>
          <p>
            Dashboards highlight adoption, satisfaction, and agent performance so we can prioritize the right enhancements.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="improvement-card">
          <h3>Prompt and policy tuning</h3>
          <p>
            Monthly review cycles refine prompts, guardrails, and automations based on real user conversations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="improvement-card">
          <h3>Cost governance</h3>
          <p>
            Spending reports and forecasting models keep GPU, storage, and data transfer costs predictable.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="improvement-card">
          <h3>Innovation backlog</h3>
          <p>
            Joint roadmap planning sessions capture new features, integrations, and experiments to tackle next.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Meet the Team Section -->
      <div class="team-section">
        <div class="team-content">
          <h2>Meet the team behind your success plan</h2>
          <p>
            We introduce the engineers, analysts, and program leads supporting your account so you know exactly who to call.
          </p>
          <a href="/#contact" class="cta-button">Start your onboarding conversation</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 4: Common Questions / FAQ (DARK + TEAL WAVE) -->
  <section class="support-faq">
    <!-- Teal wave background -->
    <div class="wave-background">
      <svg class="wave wave-1" viewBox="0 0 1440 320" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <path fill="rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.3)" d="M0,192L48,197.3C96,203,192,213,288,229.3C384,245,480,267,576,250.7C672,235,768,181,864,181.3C960,181,1056,235,1152,234.7C1248,235,1344,181,1392,154.7L1440,128L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"></path>
      </svg>
      <svg class="wave wave-2" viewBox="0 0 1440 320" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <path fill="rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.2)" d="M0,64L48,80C96,96,192,128,288,128C384,128,480,96,576,90.7C672,85,768,107,864,144C960,181,1056,235,1152,234.7C1248,235,1344,181,1392,154.7L1440,128L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="faq-title">
        Common <span class="highlight-box">questions</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do you cover nights and weekends?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Our monitoring and on-call rotations run 24/7 with the agreed SLA windows.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can we include our partners?</h3>
          <p>We will onboard MSPs, franchise operators, or vendors under your guidance with tailored permissions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What happens after the first year?</h3>
          <p>We renew support scopes annually, adjusting coverage as usage expands across teams and regions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</LayoutRedesign>

<style>
  /* ============================================
     SECTION 1: Hero + Support Fundamentals (IMAGE BACKGROUND)
     ============================================ */
  .support-hero {
    position: relative;
    background:
      linear-gradient(
        to bottom,
        rgba(10, 15, 26, 0.88) 0%,
        rgba(10, 15, 26, 0.80) 100%
      ),
      url('/images/support-hero-bg.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
    background-attachment: scroll, fixed;
    padding: 8rem 0 6rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-light-muted);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Support Fundamentals Grid */
  .fundamentals-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .fundamental-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .fundamental-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
  }

  .fundamental-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .fundamental-card p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .support-hero {
      padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    }

    .fundamentals-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* ============================================
     SECTION 2: Onboarding Timeline + Support Channels (DARK + TEAL WAVE)
     ============================================ */
  .support-onboarding {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }

  /* Teal wave background */
  .wave-background {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 60%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .wave {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .wave-1 {
    animation: wave-float 20s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .wave-2 {
    animation: wave-float 15s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }

  @keyframes wave-float {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateX(0) translateY(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateX(-20px) translateY(10px);
    }
  }

  .onboarding-grid {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .onboarding-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }

  .onboarding-timeline h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-list {
    list-style: decimal inside;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .timeline-list li {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-light-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    padding-left: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-note {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Support Channels Card */
  .support-channels-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .support-channels-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .channels-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .channels-list li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-light-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .channels-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.7em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--color-accent-secondary);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .channels-note {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ============================================
     SECTION 3: Continuous Improvement + Meet the Team (IMAGE BACKGROUND)
     ============================================ */
  .support-improvement {
    position: relative;
    background:
      linear-gradient(
        to bottom,
        rgba(10, 15, 26, 0.85) 0%,
        rgba(10, 15, 26, 0.80) 100%
      ),
      url('/images/support-improvement-bg.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
    background-attachment: scroll, fixed;
    padding: 6rem 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .improvement-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
  }

  .improvement-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .improvement-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
  }

  .improvement-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .improvement-card p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Meet the Team Section */
  .team-section {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .team-content h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .team-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-light-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-accent-primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-hover);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .support-improvement {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }

    .improvement-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* ============================================
     SECTION 4: Common Questions / FAQ (DARK + TEAL WAVE)
     ============================================ */
  .support-faq {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }

  .faq-title {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .faq-grid {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .faq-item:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-color: rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .faq-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-light-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .support-faq {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }

    .faq-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* ============================================
     Highlight Box (Lime)
     ============================================ */
  .highlight-box {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-highlight);
    color: var(--bg-dark);
    padding: 0.1em 0.3em;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  /* Container */
  .container {
    max-width: var(--container-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }
</style>
